Interface ICompositeRuleBasedValueSpecification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAbstractRuleBasedValueSpecification, IEntity, IValueSpecification

    public interface ICompositeRuleBasedValueSpecification
extends IEntity, IAbstractRuleBasedValueSpecification
    ICompositeRuleBasedValueSpecification: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents rule based values for DataPrototypes typed by composite ApplicationDataTypes.
